Write a java program to find largest of three numbers?
Step1.Take 3 number from command line.
Step2.Store the element in 3 variable.
Step4.Comapre each value with other three value if number is largest print largest Number.
:::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::
package io.javabrains;

import java.util.Scanner;

public class LargestNumberInThreeNumbers {
	public static void main(String[] args) {
		Scanner scan = new Scanner(System.in);

		System.out.println("Enter X variable:- ");
		int x = scan.nextInt();

		System.out.println("Enter Y variable:- ");
		int y = scan.nextInt();

		System.out.println("Enter Z variable:- ");
		int z = scan.nextInt();

		if (x > y && x > z) {
			System.out.println("X is largest:- " + x);
		} else if (y > x && y > z) {
			System.out.println("Y is largest:- " + y);

		} else {
			System.out.println("Z is largest:- " + z);

		}
	}
}
:::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::
Enter X variable:- 
3
Enter Y variable:- 
100
Enter Z variable:- 
200
Z is largest:- 200
